Author: notoftheearth
Text: No No no I have too much pressure at home to eat and school was going to be my release. I need school to be my safe place to not eat and not be questioned. I doubt my friends would pick up on it.

Author: mysadbitchass
Text: The thought of being busy enough to distract yourself from food is all fun and games until you're hungry from the energy you expend being so busy :(
